cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR

This paper deals with computer vision techniques for vehicle segmentation in traffic videos, which falls under the scope of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms for image processing, which could be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the performance of the algorithms using metrics, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
